{"tid":1187470,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜港父...（認真）","createTime":"2019-06-05T16:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T23:23:32.000Z","uid":243526,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d574f58de61289d098875ae7af15198fed5debe","tid":1187470,"uid":243526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:13:03.000Z","msg":"細個開始上波台果陣好撚憎港父，覺得佢勁撚on9（自認係牙古路隻狗），次次出post都必有錯別字，最近先知果D老練既9up技術／錯別字係好野黎 <br />\n<br />\n何洋達既書法能力、塑膠旺（全盛時期）既個人意志、1:6對利記既執著，都係到去左連登／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁拎勁 <br />\n<br />\n連登仔好多人都反港父，但係老實講佢既9up技術、政治觸覺、對打錯字既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家牙古路&gt;&gt;港毒之父） <br />\n<br />\n我諗港父最多都係玩多1、2年就退休，其實睇得1post得1post，好好珍惜 <br />\n<br />\n利申：高登年代BoA迷"},{"pid":"6998c45bf6e3fcefe7b0f9e60ce3adf0daedd8e4","tid":1187470,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6483bf093c4109c55161cc75646a8420171f7544","tid":1187470,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6998c45bf6e3fcefe7b0f9e60ce3adf0daedd8e4","tid":1187470,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:19:52.000Z","msg":"咩"},{"pid":"d8dfce5cda74afd08e403532a17eef369e6c6643","tid":1187470,"uid":243526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6483bf093c4109c55161cc75646a8420171f7544","tid":1187470,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6998c45bf6e3fcefe7b0f9e60ce3adf0daedd8e4","tid":1187470,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:19:52.000Z","msg":"咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"ben sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0ff57fca54e85f6e33